        <mxCell id="TU1oe2ygIfIfvKxFC6g3-4" value="&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; text-align: start; text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;Session 3 · Advanced engine features&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; text-align: start; text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; text-align: start; text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; text-align: start; text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; text-align: start; text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; text-align: start; text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; text-align: start; text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; text-align: start; text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;75 min · Prefix caching (hash chain walk), speculative decoding (n-gram → EAGLE)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; text-align: start; text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;guided decoding (FSM + xgrammar). Lab: measure TTFT drop with prefix cache on L40S.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#A27130;strokeColor=#b46504;fontFamily=Comic Sans MS;" parent="1" vertex="1">
